msgid "Krita's Magnetic Selection tool reference."
msgstr "Krita 的磁性選取區域工具參考。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:16
msgid "Magnetic Selection Tool"
msgstr "磁性選取區域工具"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:18
msgid "|toolselectmagnetic|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../<rst_epilog>:72
msgid "toolselectmagnetic"
msgstr "磁性選取區域工具"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:20
msgid ""
"This tool, represented by a magnet over a selection border, allows you to "
"make freeform :ref:`selections_basics`, but unlike the :ref:"
"`polygonal_selection_tool` or the :ref:`freehand_selection_tool`, it will "
"try to magnetically snap to sharp contrasts in your image, simplifying the "
"creation of selection drastically."
msgstr ""
"磁性選取區域工具的圖示是選取區域上有一個磁石。這個工具能夠自由地\\ :ref:"
"`selections_basics`\\ ，但是不像\\ :ref:`polygonal_selection_tool`\\ 或是\\ :"
"ref:`freehand_selection_tool`\\ 一般，這個工具會嘗試把選取邊界吸附在高對比的"
"影像上，以簡化選取區域。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:22
msgid "There are two ways to make a magnetic selection:"
msgstr "這裡有兩個磁性選取區域的方法："

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:28
msgid "Animation showing the first mode of creating a magnetic selection."
msgstr "顯示第一個模式生成一個磁性選取區域的動畫。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:30
msgid ""
"The first is to use |mouseleft| and place points or nodes of the magnetic "
"selection. To finalize your selection area you can do either |mouseleft| on "
"the first created point to complete the loop and click on it again to create "
"a selection, or press :kbd:`Enter` to end the magnetic selection or click on "
"the :guilabel:`Complete` button present in Tool Options."
msgstr ""
"首先用 |mouseleft| 來設置磁性選取區域的錨點，\\ |mouseleft| 直到要完成選取"
"時，點選第一個錨點兩次來完成選取，或是換一下 :kbd:`Enter` 來結束，又或是在工"
"具選單中點選 :guilabel:`完成` 按鈕。"

#: ../../<rst_epilog>:2
msgid "mouseleft"
msgstr "滑鼠左鍵"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:36
msgid ""
"Animation showing the second (interactive) mode of creating a magnetic "
"selection."
msgstr "顯示第二種模式（交互模式）生成一個磁性選取區域的動畫。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:38
msgid ""
"The second, interactive mode, is to |mouseleft| :kbd:`+ drag` over a portion "
"of an image."
msgstr ""
"第二個模式，交互模式，在影像中\\ |mouseleft| :kbd:`+ 拖曳`\\ 以選取區域。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:44
msgid "The first and second mode can be mixed."
msgstr "第一種模式和第二種模式可以一起使用。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:46
msgid ""
"You can edit previous points by |mouseleft| dragging them. You can remove "
"points by dragging it out of the canvas area. After a path is closed. Points "
"can be undone with :kbd:`Shift + Z`. A halfway done magnetic selection can "
"be canceled with :kbd:`Esc` or clicking on the :guilabel:`Discard` button in "
"the Tool Options."
msgstr ""
"你可以透過 |mouseleft| 拖曳之前節點來編輯選取區域。把錨點拉出畫布外可以把錨點"
"移除。當路徑封閉後，可以按 :kbd:`Shift + Z` 來返回上一步。一個未完成的磁性選"
"取可以按 :kbd:`Esc`或是在工具選項按 :guilabel:`取消` 按鈕。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:50
msgid ""
"Most of the behavior of the Magnetic Selection Tool is common to all other "
"selection tools, please make sure to read :ref:`selections_basics` to learn "
"more about this tool."
msgstr ""
"磁性選取區域工具大多數動作和其他選取區域工具相似，請詳閱\\ :ref:"
"`selections_basics`\\ 以取得使用這個工具的更多資訊。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:55
msgid "Hotkeys and Sticky keys"
msgstr "快捷鍵和相黏鍵"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:57
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'add'. You can "
"release the :kbd:`Shift` key while dragging, but it will still be set to "
"'add'. Same for the others."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| 設定選取操作為「相加」。在拖曳時能夠放開 :kbd:"
"`Shift` 鍵，但是操作會還是「相加」，其他的操作類同。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:58
msgid ":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'subtract'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| 設定選取操作為「減去」。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:59
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'replace'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| 設定選取操作為「取代」。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:60
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to "
"'intersect'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| 設定選取操作為「相交」。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:64
msgid ""
"Hovering your cursor over the dashed line of the selection, or marching ants "
"as it is commonly called, turns the cursor into the move tool icon, which "
"you |mouseleft| and drag to move the selection."
msgstr ""
"把游標移到選取區域的虛線時，游標會顯示成移動工具圖示，這時候可以 |mouseleft| "
"然後拖曳選取區域。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:65
msgid ""
"|mouseright| will open up a selection quick menu with amongst others the "
"ability to edit the selection."
msgstr "|mouseright| 會開啟一個快速選單，裡面會有修改選取區域的選項。"

#: ../../<rst_epilog>:4
msgid "mouseright"
msgstr "滑鼠右鍵"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:None
msgid "Menu of magnetic selection"
msgstr "磁性選取區域工具選單"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:73
msgid ""
"You can switch the behavior of the :kbd:`Alt` key to use :kbd:`Ctrl` instead "
"by toggling the switch in Tool Settings in the :ref:`general_settings`."
msgstr ""
"你可以在 Krita 的\\ :ref:`general_settings`\\ 裡交換 :kbd:`Alt` 鍵和 :kbd:"
"`Ctrl` 鍵的修飾鍵功能。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:77
msgid ""
"This tool is not bound to any Hotkey, if you want to define one, go to :"
"menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita --> Keyboard Shortcuts` and "
"search for 'Magnetic Selection Tool', there you can select the shortcut you "
"want. Check :ref:`shortcut_settings` for more info."
msgstr ""
"這個工具預設並沒有綁定任何快捷鍵，如果想要設定一個，在\\ :menuselection:`設"
"定 --> 設定 Krita --> 鍵盤快捷鍵`\\ 然後搜尋「手繪選取區域工具」，在這裡可以"
"設定你想要的快捷鍵。在\\ :ref:`shortcut_settings`\\ 取得更多資訊。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:81
msgid "Tool Options"
msgstr "工具選項"

