msgstr "這個選項在\\ :ref:`pixel_vector_selection`\\ 中已被解釋。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:85
msgid "Action"
msgstr "操作"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:87
msgid "Anti-aliasing"
msgstr "反鋸齒"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:88
msgid ""
"This toggles whether or not to give selections feathered edges. Some people "
"prefer hard-jagged edges for their selections."
msgstr "這個選項控制是否要羽化邊緣。有些人會想要選取鋸齒狀的邊緣。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:89
msgid "Filter Radius:"
msgstr "過濾半徑："

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:90
msgid ""
"Determine the radius of the edge detection kernel. This determines how "
"aggressively the tool will interpret contrasts. Low values mean only the "
"sharpest of contrast will be a seen as an edge. High values will pick up on "
"subtle contrasts. The range of which is from 2.5 to 100."
msgstr ""
"這個數值控制邊緣判定的範圍。這個數值決定這個工具在對比度判斷的激進程度。數值"
"較低時只有最明顯的對比會判斷為邊緣。數值較高時細微的對比會判斷為邊緣。數值範"
"圍在 2.5 到 100 之間。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:91
msgid "Threshold:"
msgstr "閾值："

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:92
msgid ""
"From 0 to 255, how sharp your edge is, 0 is least while 255 is the most. "
"Used in the interactive mode only."
msgstr ""
"從 0 到 255，判斷邊緣的銳利度，0 是最不銳利，255 最銳利。只能在交互模式使用。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:93
msgid "Search Radius:"
msgstr "搜尋半徑："

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:94
msgid ""
"The area in which the tool will search for a sharp contrast within an image. "
"More pixels means less precision is needed when placing the points, but this "
"will require Krita to do more work, and thus slows down the tool."
msgstr ""
"這個數值決定工具在影像中搜尋銳利邊緣的範圍大小。更大的範圍表示在放錨點時需要"
"更少的精確度，但是這樣的話 Krita 需要運算更久，因而減慢這個工具的速度。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:103
msgid "Anchor Gap:"
msgstr "錨點間距："

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:96
msgid ""
"When using |mouseleft| :kbd:`+ drag` to place points automatically, this "
"value determines the average gap between 2 anchors. Low values give high "
"precision by placing many nodes, but this is also harder to edit afterwards. "
"The pixels are in screen dimensions and not image dimensions, meaning it is "
"affected by zoom."
msgstr ""
"在使用 |mouseleft| 拖曳時會自動放置錨點，這個數值會判斷兩個錨點之間的平均間"
"距。數值較低時因錨點較多而精確度更高，但是這樣會導致後續修改困難。數值判斷是"
"螢幕顯示的面積而非影像面積，這代表著這個數值會因縮放影響。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:102
msgid "To the **left**: 20 px anchor gap, to the **right**: 40px anchor gap."
msgstr "**左邊**\\ ：20 px 錨點間距；\\ **右邊**\\ ：40 px 錨點間距。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/magnetic_select.rst:107
msgid "Anti-aliasing is only available on Pixel Selection Mode."
msgstr "反鋸齒只能像素選取區域模式中使用。"

